<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10698>
    dc:description "Figure 3. The newly described Melicope balgooyi Appelhans, W. L. Wagner & K. R. Wood. A Flowering branch B Leaf with detailed venation C Pistillate inflorescence [peduncle not shown in full length] D Single staminate flower. Based on K. R. Wood 9727 (PTBG, A-C) and K. R. Wood 9698 (PTBG, D)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10698" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10699>
    dc:description "Figure 4. A Habit of Melicope balgooyi Appelhans, W. L. Wagner & K. R. Wood in situ B Habitat of Melicope balgooyi around the steep precipitous slopes of Pokumaru, Rapa, Austral Islands." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/10699" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

